{"tid":1378750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對於附近大廈同樓上街坊 我表示無盡感激","createTime":"2019-07-28T16:35:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T16:47:26.000Z","uid":2617,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"70dfa385fbc7a52bf19fa3d942bed83e1f79dcf9","tid":1378750,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:35:51.000Z","msg":"岩岩樓下發生無差別大火<br />\n好多人大逃亡四散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n沿途有好多車內司機話比我地知邊到有火頭<br />\n大廈D保安教晒我地邊到有位換番防火衣物<br />\n同埋點樣搵到最快離開火場既方法<br />\n有樓上街坊甚至落埋黎問我地駛唔駛上去暫避<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔知佢地內心會唔會怪責有人玩火<br />\n但係呢一班咁善心既街坊同市民<br />\n都好有心幫大家離開火場<br />\n大家先唔駛葬身火海<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我黑B係呢到<br />\n向佢地予以最崇高既敬意 無盡感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"e892316531906f1c865365f6cefc8d6b73d54770","tid":1378750,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:38:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e9ec6903ec6ae5096b45fd0e1963eec9add1602","tid":1378750,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:40:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10467f017666c5b13c1042bdd0feda8b8cacad9d","tid":1378750,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0